"'''A Grand Admiral Returns'''" is a short story written by [[Bill Slavicsek]], originally published in the ''[[Heir to the Empire Sourcebook]]'' and later archived on [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]]. The story is set [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]].

==Plot summary==
Captain [[Gilad Pellaeon/Legends|Gilad Pellaeon]] awaits news from a mysterious contact that has ordered his Star Destroyer, [[Chimaera/Legends|''Chimaera'']], to a meeting in space. Pellaeon is then surprised when the contact proves to be a [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|blue-skinned alien]] who announces himself as a [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] and proclaims that the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire's]] fortunes are about to change for the better.

